Requirements: - `to` cannot be the zero address. - `from` must have at least `amount` of `id`. - `ids` and `amounts` must have the same length. - If the caller is not `from`,   it must be approved to manage the tokens of `from`. - If `to` refers to a smart contract, it must implement   {ERC1155-onERC1155BatchReveived}, which is called upon a batch transfer. Emits a {TransferBatch} event.
